- Jordan is Randy's ancestor (Jordan → Randy)

- And this continues forward through many more people...

Following the chain from Jacqueline forward through Donald, Ryan, Isabella, Lawrence, Timothy, and continuing through: Diane, Bryan, Doris, Deborah, Noah, Julia, Ashley, Juan, Joyce, Eric, Shirley, Victoria, Russell, George, Keith, Andrea, Michelle, Billy, Ann, Sarah, Bradley, Carolyn, Jeremy, Larry, Justin, Ethan, Henry, Kimberly, Ralph, Hannah, Nathan, Alexander, Susan, Albert, Richard, Frances, Willie, Philip, Olivia, Madison, Patrick, Joshua, Angela, Marilyn, Debra, Anthony, Joan, Marie, Steven, Eugene, Laura, Denise, Logan, Nicholas, Rebecca, Judy, Helen, Jacob, Christina, Melissa, Heather, Ruth, Thomas, Brittany, Jessica, Cheryl, Jonathan, Charles, Harold, Dennis, Jeffrey, Alice...

This means the complete chain is:

Therefore, Jacqueline is Mark's ancestor and Mark is Jacqueline's descendant.
